original_title: Gabrielle ou le saut de l’ange
overview: Bruno, thirty-five, married, two children, becomes Gabrielle after ten years of suffering, doubt, but also determination. Gabrielle is now 50 years old. She has no regrets except the great pain of not seeing her children anymore. Ten long years to change sex, but how many years to "live" finally. What does it take to have the acceptance of others, of herself, of her family ...?
title: Gabrielle ou le saut de l’ange
